1 (3) Debt service on the Authority's revenue bonds or related purposes such as the
2 establishment of debt service reserve funds.
3 (4) Debt service, debt service reserve funds, and other financing costs related to
4 any of the following:
5 a. A financing undertaken by a private entity under a partnership
6 agreement with the entity for the Project.
7 b. Private activity bonds issued under law related to the Project.
8 c. Any federal or State loan, line of credit, or loan guarantee relating to
9 the Project.
10 (5) A return on investment of any private entity under a partnership agreement
11 with the entity for the Project.
12 (6) Any other uses granted to a private entity under a partnership agreement with
13 the entity for the Project."
