15 REVISIONS TO BRIDGE PROGRAM OUTSOURCING
16 SECTION 9. G.S. 136-76.2(c) reads as rewritten:
17 "(c) Outsourcing. – Except for the following activities, all projects funded under the bridge
18 program established under subsection (a) of this section shall be outsourced to private
19 contractors:
20 (1) Inspection.
21 (2) Pre-engineering.
22 (3) Contract preparation.
23 (4) Contract administration and oversight.
24 (5) Planning activities.
25 (6) Installation of culverts and structures described in subsection (b) of this
26 section, but only in cases of emergency.section on low volume or non-outlet
27 roads."
